[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0438","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0438.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0253","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 ASP 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 在安装 iis-fix 热修复补丁后存在源码泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 中使用 %2e 替代点号（.）绕过补丁限制，直接读取 ASP 程序源代码。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致数据库连接字符串、业务逻辑等敏感信息泄露，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0253"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.503","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 提供的 IIS 3.0 安全补丁 (Q164301)，或升级至 IIS 4.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可部署 URLScan 工具拦截包含 %2e 的 URL 请求，或在 ISAPI 过滤器中添加规则对 %2e 进行规范化校验，防止编码绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1814","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0253.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0253","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0253.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0253.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0253.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jq56-hqwg-c6vv/GHSA-jq56-hqwg-c6vv.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0253.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/asp_source_dot.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0253.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0438.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0449","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0449.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0265","title":"Novell NetWare 3.12 ICMP Redirect Message 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 3.12 操作系统在处理 ICMP 重定向消息时存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20）。远程攻击者可向目标主机发送特制的 ICMP 重定向数据包，触发系统处理异常，导致目标系统崩溃或挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，攻击复杂度低，影响 Novell NetWare 3.12 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0265"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.977","remediation":"建议升级至 Novell Open Enterprise Server (OES) 当前维护版本以获得完整安全支持。如暂无法升级，可在 NetWare 服务器上通过设置 SET ALLOW ICMP REDIRECT = OFF 禁用 ICMP 重定向处理；同时在网络边界防火墙配置规则，丢弃入站的 ICMP 类型 5（重定向）报文，以阻断远程攻击路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ154174","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0265.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0265","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/icmp.rules","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0265.md","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/473.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.386"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0449.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0460","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0460.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0274","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 DNS Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 DNS 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标服务器发送一个未经请求的恶意 DNS 应答数据包，由于服务器未对该应答与待处理查询进行匹配验证，处理该异常响应时会导致服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，造成正常的域名解析服务中断。攻击者无需认证即可远程触发该漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0274"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.090","remediation":"升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 4 及以上版本，或在 DNS 服务器上配置仅响应来自可信上游 DNS 的查询请求，并在边界防火墙上过滤源端口 53 的非授权 DNS 响应数据包，防止伪造 DNS 应答触发拒绝服务。如无法升级，建议将 DNS 服务迁移至 Windows 2000 Server 或后续受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0274","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0274.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0274.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0274","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0274.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0274.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0274.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5q47-xw9h-8mx2/GHSA-5q47-xw9h-8mx2.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0274.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0460.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0564","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0564.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0345","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 ICMP Jolt 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 的 ICMP 协议处理存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，可通过向目标系统发送特制的分片 ICMP 数据包（即 Jolt 攻击），触发系统在处理畸形 IP 分片重组时产生资源耗尽或内核崩溃，导致目标系统蓝屏死机或完全停止响应。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 版本，属于经典的 IP 分片攻击方式。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0345"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.867","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-035 提供的补丁，或升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6 及以上版本；Windows 95 用户应安装 Winsock2 更新。如无法打补丁，建议在网络边界防火墙或主机 IPSec 策略中丢弃恶意分片 ICMP 数据包，防止畸形 IP 分片到达目标系统。彻底解决需升级至受支持的 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/62170","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0345.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0345","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0345.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0345.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pwf4-g7fv-h2w4/GHSA-pwf4-g7fv-h2w4.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7c1bf0db-8de4-4873-82bc-3461101fb8a2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0345.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0564.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0750","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0750.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0499","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 SNMP NetBIOS 共享信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统中，NetBIOS 共享信息可能通过 SNMP 注册表项被非授权泄露。远程攻击者可利用 SNMP 服务查询目标系统的注册表，获取 NetBIOS 共享名称、路径等敏感信息，为后续攻击提供侦察基础。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 版本，攻击者只需能够访问目标系统的 SNMP 服务（默认端口 161/162）即可利用，无需身份认证。建议禁用不必要的 SNMP 服务或限制 SNMP 访问权限以降低风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0499"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.723","remediation":"升级到 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本系统，或在 SNMP 服务配置中将注册表项 HKLM\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\SNMP\\Parameters 的权限设置为仅允许管理员访问，同时在防火墙上限制 UDP 161/162 端口的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0499"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0750.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0753","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0753.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0503","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 账户可猜测密码漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统中存在用户账户密码强度不足的漏洞，本地用户或管理员账户若设置了弱口令或默认密码，攻击者可通过暴力破解或字典攻击等方���获取系统访问权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 等版本，允许已获得本地访问权限的攻击者提升权限或横向移动。建议使用强密码策略并启用账户锁定机制以降低风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0503"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.083","remediation":"通过本地安全策略（secpol.msc）启用密码必须符合复杂性要求策略，设置密码长度最小值至少 8 个字符，密码最长使用期限不超过 90 天，并启用账户锁定阈值（5 次无效登录后锁定 30 分钟）。对于已停服的 Windows NT/2000 系统，建议迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并部署 Active Directory 组策略统一实施密码策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0503","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0503.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0503","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0503.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0503.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/bbd7116272e853f39577ba54522637fe18ed9411/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/brampat/security/blob/41c178323fcaa886c7e5cea6297a6d2391d35b00/defense/passwords/README.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0503.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0753.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0754","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0754.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0504","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 本地用户账户默认空密码权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中存在默认、空值、空白或缺失密码的本地用户或管理员账户漏洞，攻击者可通过枚举或暴力破解等方式利用空密码或默认密码直接登录目标系统，获取系统控制权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击者可借助 Metasploit 等工具框架中的认证用户代码执行模块实施远程利用，无需额外认证绕过。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0504"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.193","remediation":"为所有 Windows NT 本地用户和管理员账户设置复杂密码（至少 8 位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符）。启用本地安全策略中的密码复杂度要求和账户锁定阈值（如 5 次失败即锁定 30 分钟）。通过组策略禁用 Guest 账户，并定期审计所有本地账户密码状态。对于 Windows Server，可在安全模板中启用密码必须满足复杂性要求策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0504","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16374","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0504.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0504","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0504.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0504.json","https://github.com/vulncheck-oss/0day.today.archive/blob/3664abdd71985a44aff3260896a8f36e2f4a9682/remote-exploits/20991.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce70cbcf8165046f2229cbe0d9f53c47bf63ece0/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4cc2-25hc-9x3v/GHSA-4cc2-25hc-9x3v.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_login_as_users.nasl","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/cve_2_MSF_exploit_Mapping/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/dradis/dradis-nexpose/blob/fe9333a24a7a643ff8ddf64588baac4a9062fc0a/templates/full_vulnerability.sample"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0754.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0764","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0764.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0510","title":"路由器或防火墙 IP源路由绕过漏洞","description":"IP 源路由选项（Loose Source and Record Route / Strict Source Routing）允许数据包发送方指定途经路径。当路由器或防火墙未正确过滤携带源路由选项的 IP 数据包时，远程攻击者可绕过正常的路由策略和访问控制规则，伪造可信源地址，将数据包强制路由至本不可达的内部网络，进而实施网络探测、中间人攻击或越权访问。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS v2.0 评分 7.5，危害等级高。缓解措施包括在网络边界设备上禁用 IP 源路由选项的转发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0510"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.890","remediation":"在路由器或防火墙上禁用 IP 源路由功能：Cisco 设备使用 `no ip source-route` 命令，Linux 系统设置 `net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_source_route=0`，Windows 系统将注册表 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters\\DisableIPSourceRouting` 设为 2。同时确保边界 ACL 过滤源路由选项（IP Option 3）的数据包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0510","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2f8583cd0e244c401900c481a78c07fe5535c09f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0510.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0510","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0510.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0510.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8d306744aeef0a134e581249fd492603b0e6795d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5f97-65cc-4xfc/GHSA-5f97-65cc-4xfc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0510.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83214/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0764.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0765","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0765.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0511","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 IP 转发默认启用信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统默认或错误配置启用了 IP 转发功能，导致非路由器或防火墙的普通主机充当网络层转发节点。远程攻击者可利用此配置缺陷，通过该主机转发数据包绕过网络访问控制策略，实现内网探测、中间人攻击或信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，CVSS 评分 9.1，危害等级严重。修复建议为在非路由场景下禁用 IP 转发功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0511"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.007","remediation":"在非路由器的 Windows NT/2000 系统上，通过注册表将 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters\\IPEnableRouter` 值设为 0，或通过网络连接属性取消勾选「启用 IP 转发」。同时建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本以获得更完善的安全机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0511","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0511.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2f8583cd0e244c401900c481a78c07fe5535c09f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0511.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0511","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/5a9570703da14a2b5eac448afa9c83878dd7f663/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0511.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0511.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/78eafd4564fbf54df959d50d6817c30fd8606422/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3fwm-5x3q-64xf/GHSA-3fwm-5x3q-64xf.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0511.json","https://github.com/Hurley2017/mulval_updated/blob/eeb3da1975075e62db42cbfde5b4a8a3e9f35654/CustomTests/HomeWiFi/vulInfo.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83204/info.html","https://github.com/hadousoftware/base-images/blob/ab6afc9661bbd001d8be8fdc4ac1a3fdd8d1e824/base/abi/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0765.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0772","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0772.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0518","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 NETBIOS/SMB 共享口令可猜测漏洞","description":"Windows 95 系统的 NETBIOS/SMB 共享存在弱口令或可猜测密码漏洞，攻击者可利用字典攻击或暴力破解方式猜测共享资源的访问密码，进而未经授权访问目标系统的共享文件夹和文件。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 及早期 Windows 系统，攻击条件较低，只需网络可达即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0518"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.983","remediation":"Windows 95 系统已停止支持且无官方补丁，建议立即升级到受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）；如无法升级，在网络边界防火墙封禁 TCP 139/445 及 UDP 137/138 端口阻断 SMB 协议暴露，同时在本地网络属性中禁用\"Microsoft 网络的文件和打印机共享\"，并为共享文件夹设置 14 位以上强密码（含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0518"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0772.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0778","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0778.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0521","title":"Sun NIS 网域名称可猜测信息泄露漏洞","description":"NIS（网络信息服务，原名 Yellow Pages）协议存在安全设计缺陷，其域名通常为固定格式或可被轻易猜测。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过爆破或猜测 NIS 域名后，向目标系统的 ypserv 服务发送请求，获取 passwd、shadow、hosts 等关键映射信息。成功利用可导致用户密码哈希、主机配置等敏感数据泄露，为后续横向移动和权限提升创造有利条件。该漏洞影响所有启用 NIS 机制的系统（主要为 Unix/Linux 环境），属于经典的敏感信息泄露漏洞。修复措施包括限制 NIS 服务网络暴露面、使用 ypsec 安全机制或迁移至 LDAP 等更安全的替代方案。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0521"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.360","remediation":"将 NIS 域名设置为难以猜测的复杂字符串（至少 16 位，含大小写字母和数字），切勿使用默认或与组织信息相关的域名。在 /etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny 中限制能访问 NIS 服务的客户端 IP 范围，仅允许受信网段。如条件允许，建议迁移至 LDAP/Kerberos 等更安全的集中认证方案替代 NIS。iptables 层面仅放行必要端口（111/TCP/UDP 的 portmap 及 834/TCP/UDP 的 ypserv）的白名单来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-13.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0778.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0782","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0782.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0525","title":"多种厂商 IP 协议 Traceroute 路由跟踪信息泄露漏洞","description":"IP 路由跟踪功能默认允许来自任意主机的探测请求，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过发送 TTL 递增的 ICMP 或 UDP 数据包逐跳探测目标网络的路由路径，从而获取网络拓扑结构、内部 IP 地址段及中间网关信息。此类信息泄露可为后续定向攻击提供侦察支撑，扩大攻击面。建议在网络边界配置防火墙规则限制 ICMP 时间超时响应，或禁用不必要的路由跟踪响应来缓解该风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0525"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.923","remediation":"在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），过滤入站 ICMP Time Exceeded 报文（ICMP type 11），或直接禁用从外网发起的 traceroute 请求（UDP 端口 33434-33534、ICMP Echo 及 TCP 高端口探测）。在 Linux 系统可设置 `sysctl -w net.ipv4.icmp_ignore_bogus_error_responses=1` 降低信息泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0525"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0782.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0802","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0802.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0534","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 用户权限不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT/2000 存在用户权限分配不当的安全漏洞，系统管理员可能为普通用户授予了过高的系统权限，包括作为操作系统的一部分、添加工作站、备份文件和目录、更改系统时间、创建页面文件、调试程序、生成安全审计、增加配额、加载卸载设备驱动程序、锁定内存页、获取文件或其他对象的所有权等特权。本地用户可利用获得的过高权限绕过安全限制，执行未经授权的系统操作，进而影响系统完整性和机密性。此漏洞源于 Windows NT/2000 权限模型中对用户权限的细粒度控制不足，攻击者需具有本地访问权限才能利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0534"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:35.877","remediation":"审核并移除不必要的用户权限分配，打开「管理工具 → 本地安全策略 → 用户权限指派」，逐项检查「作为操作系统的一部分」「调试程序」「取得文件或其他对象的所有权」等权限，仅分配给 Administrators 组。由于 Windows NT/2000 已停止支持，强烈建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016+，并在升级前通过组策略限制用户权限遵循最小权限原则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0534"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0802.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0803","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0803.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0535","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 密码策略配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统的账户密码策略存在安全配置不当缺陷，密码长度、密码最长使用期限及密码唯一性等关键安全参数未合理设置。攻击者可利用弱密码策略通过暴力破解或字典攻击手段获取合法用户账户权限，从而实现对目标系统的未授权访问。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000，系统管理员需手动修正密码策略配置以消除风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0535"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.003","remediation":"通过「管理工具→本地安全策略→账户策略→密码策略」配置：密码长度最小值≥8个字符、密码最长使用期限≤90天、强制密码历史≥5个（防止重复使用最近密码）、密码必须符合复杂性要求（启用）。在域环境中通过组策略统一部署。同时禁用空白密码。该配置适用于 Windows NT 4.0/2000/XP 及后续版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0535"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0803.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0814","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0550","title":"路由器路由表远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"部分路由器设备配置不当或存在权限校验缺陷，导致任意远程主机无需认证即可通过特定协议查询并获取路由器的完整路由表信息。攻击者可借此掌握目标网络的拓扑结构、子网划分及可达路径，为后续针对性网络攻击（如中间人攻击、路由劫持）提供侦察基础。该漏洞危害等级高，影响多种主流路由器设备，CVSS 评分 7.5。建议限制 SNMP 等管理协议的访问来源，配置 ACL 规则以限制路由信息查询权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0550"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.973","remediation":"在路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），仅允许信任的管理网段访问 SNMP、Telnet/SSH 及 Web 管理端口；关闭未使用的 SNMP 服务或将 SNMP 字符串设为只读并改用复杂 community 字符串；禁用路由协议的明文邻居通告（如 Cisco 路由器使用 `no ip route-cache same-interface` 配合 `distribute-list` 过滤路由表查询）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0550"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml"}]